---
import Pre from '@/components/pre.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
---

<section class='flex flex-col lg:h-svh lg:flex-row items-center w-11/12 py-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl'>
  <div class='w-full pb-6 sm:pb-8 lg:pb-0 lg:pr-40'>
    <h2 class='text-4xl pb-6 md:pb-8 font-bold 2xl:text-5xl'>About me</h2>

    <div class='max-w-2xl text-neutral-100 space-y-4 md:space-y-6'>
      <Pre>
        You asked for it, it looks like you are interested in my story, please read my cv if you
        prefer my career journey only.
      </Pre>
      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        My name is Rizki Maulana Citra, you can call me <code
          class='bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground py-0.5 px-1 rounded'
          >Rizki, Iki-or Citra</code
        >, I have been learning programming since when I was at High School, precisely at 17.
      </p>

      <p class='text-neutral-400 font-medium'>
        I was raised by a small family near Pulosari Mountain. It is a very good place, fresh air,
        rice fields, rivers, you named it, everything is beautiful.
      </p>

      <Pre>The scenery is just like a heaven if you asked me.</Pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <figure class='max-lg:w-full'>
    <Image
      inferSize
      loading='lazy'
      decoding='async'
      class='lg:ml-auto h-96 lg:h-80 w-full lg:w-96 object-cover rounded'
      src='https://res.cloudinary.com/rizkicitra/image/upload/v1717282063/potrait.jpg'
      alt='A potrait of Rizki'
      title='A potrait of Rizki'
    />
    <figcaption class='text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400 pt-2'>
      <em>A potrait of Rizki</em>
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
</section>
